{"tid":891641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【行路到美國】難民大隊抵墨西哥城 居民捐衣物鞋履支援","createTime":"2018-11-06T09:42:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T10:58:47.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e5721e6d6179edaaeb5cbdc6902e9b9ac492d57e","tid":891641,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:42:37.000Z","msg":"打算到美國的中美洲難民大隊周日抵達墨西哥首都墨西哥城，距離最近的美國德州過境關口尚有805公里。當地政府開放體育場讓他們棲息、享用食物及醫療服務；美國總統特朗普派往邊境的數千兵力，則忙於架設起帶刺鐵絲網，嚴陣以待。<br />\n在著名景點瓜達露佩聖母聖殿外，有義工用擴音器邀請難民乘坐巴士，前往體育場休息，又有居民捐出衣服及鞋子支援他們。當地政府已在體育場準備好食物、1萬公升食水、醫療及法律服務接待這批約千名的難民。<br />\n難民為逃離家鄉的暴力問題及經濟窘境，不惜步行千里。雖然特朗普明言不歡迎他們，但大隊決心未減。冀帶着6歲兒子由洪都拉斯前往美國的曼西利亞指，「我們正昂首走到美國，去實現我們的美國夢。我對主有信心，無論在甚麼情況下，我也會這樣做」。<br />\n美國政府連日要求墨西哥攔截難民。墨西哥政府宣佈若難民在當地申請庇護，會為他們辦理臨時身份及安排工作。現時當局已遣返1,100多人，並正處理2,800宗庇護申請。來自危地馬拉的難民戈麥斯指「首先會嘗試進入美國，若不可行，可能會留在這裏」。<br />\n路透社"},{"pid":"bdf342c97604854ecb3d28dacbee3429222a096f","tid":891641,"uid":96486,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:43:58.000Z","msg":"咁撚大愛又唔養起佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c30295f95e3316b2def1babbcbe4e7f24b5b230e","tid":891641,"uid":21984,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:44:12.000Z","msg":"偷渡偷到攞正牌咁<br />\n仲有義工嗰下好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6342625013a70e85e5797da84329947fbd2de85e","tid":891641,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:44:36.000Z","msg":"好像理所當然，唔望俾墨佬賣曬做雞"},{"pid":"544047d3efb7c00736ae49d035c00a737bc0951d","tid":891641,"uid":40763,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:45:19.000Z","msg":"講撚到明唔歡迎你都要仆埋去<br />\n夾硬達陣 美國用武力又話自己手無寸鐵<br />\n留係墨西哥算鳩數啦 人地開放埋俾你<br />\n正仆街"},{"pid":"1f2ae9781673ffaa0c66bdf12dd26b4acb90d108","tid":891641,"uid":72581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:01:05.000Z","msg":"憑咩自稱難民？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc32dd26eafa464a7bb80e041596972af998ccfc","tid":891641,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f2ae9781673ffaa0c66bdf12dd26b4acb90d108","tid":891641,"uid":72581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:01:05.000Z","msg":"憑咩自稱難民？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:02:00.000Z","msg":"爛民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dddbb3287d0bd1f2d03beadc0f235d0f5c1ead6","tid":891641,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc32dd26eafa464a7bb80e041596972af998ccfc","tid":891641,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f2ae9781673ffaa0c66bdf12dd26b4acb90d108","tid":891641,"uid":72581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:01:05.000Z","msg":"憑咩自稱難民？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:02:00.000Z","msg":"爛民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:44:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f75e36f2a2b9eebdb28b70d2195a0834a385fe","tid":891641,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:51:23.000Z","msg":"難民來了齊帶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc7de8a2f4b4cf3489b02d3b4f158e7f71c2fad","tid":891641,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:54:01.000Z","msg":"首批只係幾百人<br />\n<br />\n香港一日150人"},{"pid":"22ff9708fd5348a500f5b0648b570ee9c5ce6c67","tid":891641,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:58:47.000Z","msg":"墨西哥居民捐衣物鞋履支援 , 因為想你快啲走"}]}